{"article_id":"Zxeqtz92JvDPlB2l","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"U.S. Rep. Richard Neal got a political slap in the face","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"- instead of the usual slap on the back -","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"from Democratic colleagues","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"when he filed a lawsuit Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"demanding President Trump ' s tax information .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"\" This should have been done a long time ago","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and the delay has really - really means","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that probably we see none of this this year , \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"complained U.S. Rep. Lloyd Doggett","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"( D-Texas )","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"while on CNN on Tuesday night .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Neal filed a lawsuit","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"demanding access to six years of Trump ' s tax returns .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Doggett , part of the progressive wing of Democrats inside the House of Representatives , sits on the Ways and Means Committee","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"chaired by Neal .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" Being dilatory is not good","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"when your opponent ' s tactic is delay , delay , delay , \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Doggett added .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Neal , as chairman , has the authority","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"to demand Trump ' s tax returns .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"He asked the IRS for the information in April ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and filed subpoenas in May .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"\" Due to that noncompliance , the Committee is now pursuing this matter in the federal courts , \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Neal said Tuesday in a statement","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"announcing his legal action .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Lawmakers and even members of the media voiced outrage , however ,","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"that the Springfield Democrat took so long .","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"\" Neal has been totally asleep at the switch .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"It ' s July .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Where has he been ? \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"said CNN legal analyst Jeffery Toobin .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"\" This is actually a very simple case","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that should have been filed in February , not in July","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and now it ' s gon na be in the district court , in the circuit court and maybe in the Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Who knows","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"if it will even be resolved before the next presidential election , \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Toobin said on CNN Tuesday night .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"The outrage suggests","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"the 70-year-old Neal could find himself targeted","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"as a growing number of establishment Democrats have been for ouster by younger , liberal candidates .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Somerville Democrat Michael Capuano , a self-described progressive incumbent","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"who was beaten by U.S. Rep. Ayanna Pressley in 2018 ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"is the most recent example .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Neal has already been singled out by the Progressive Change Campaign Committee , a group","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"that supported U.S. Sen. Elizabeth Warren and New York Congresswoman Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"\" Anyone","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"paying attention","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"knows","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that he stood in the way","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"of requesting Trump ' s tax returns , \"","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"said Adam Green , PCCC co-founder .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"\" A primary would be very healthy in his district","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"because local voters deserve better . \"","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Neal spokesman William Tranghese referred to Tuesday ' s release","depth":3},{"id":54,"text":"when asked about the criticisms .","depth":3},{"id":55,"text":"But","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"considering the grim fate of other long-serving Dems ,","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"the dean of the Massachusetts delegation might want to heed the warnings of his lefty colleagues","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"if he wants to remain on Capitol Hill .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":117,"left":111,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":95,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":83,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":76,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":69,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":63,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":60,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":60,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":65,"right":67,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":64,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":67,"left":66,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":66,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":70,"right":74,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":71,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"context","nu